# ✨ Air Canvas – Draw with Your Fingertip

Air Canvas is a gesture-based drawing tool that lets you create art in mid-air using your index finger and a webcam.

## 🚀 Features
- Fingertip tracking using MediaPipe
- Real-time drawing on a virtual canvas
- Press `c` to clear
- Press `s` to save your drawing
- Press `ESC` to exit

## 🛠️ Technologies
- Python
- OpenCV
- MediaPipe
- NumPy

